That can be done just like in the signle palyer version. Using 'foreground &lt;#RRGGBB&gt;' replacing RRGGBB with the hexy code for the colour you want, or typing the name of the colour. You can use '|xn' to keep the line going. Example:[code:1coh3v53]foreground &lt;#AA550F&gt;
msg &lt;You see a |xn&gt;
foreground &lt;blue&gt;
msg &lt;Banana!!!&gt;[/code:1coh3v53]Need anything else just ask me.
